column2: ALPHA BLACK TO PAPA BEAR. WE GOT THE TOWN, I REPEAT WE GOT THE TOWN. OVER.
ALPHA TO PAPA BEAR. SHILKA IS DOWN I REPEAT SHILKA IS DOWN. OVER.
ALPHA BLACK TO BRAVO BLACK. NOMAD STICK I REPEAT NOMAD STICK. OVER.
CHARLIE BLACK TO PAPA BEAR. WERE DONE HERE. GOING TO REARM. SEND IN DELTA. OVER.
DELTA BLACK TO PAPA BEAR. SEEK AND DESTROY COMPLETE. DOING REARMING. DISPATCH CHARLIE. OVER.
PAPA BEAR TO ALPHA. EXCELLENT JOB CONGRATULATIONS. OVER.
